<p begin="24350000t" end="39250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle0">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="40370000t" end="73360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle1">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="74400000t" end="142430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle2">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="260590000t" end="303930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle3">&#x202a;果實宣告了未知的將來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="304970000t" end="374600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle4">&#x202a;夢想蛻變成理想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="415080000t" end="496430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle5">&#x202a;任誰都渴望落幕…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="516840000t" end="532080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle6">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="533190000t" end="565840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle7">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="566890000t" end="618540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle8">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="619610000t" end="669210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;總有一天我會讓你看到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="670330000t" end="732330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;光輝閃耀的世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="801130000t" end="831050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;第14話 朋友&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="893220000t" end="907890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;我知道了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="908900000t" end="939840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;雖然不能當你的男友&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;但我會努力扮演的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="952280000t" end="968200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;謝謝你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="969300000t" end="995580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;我會努力讓你喜歡上我的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1013340000t" end="1035640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;讓她去看L的臉&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1036700000t" end="1081640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;知道L的名字後&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;將搜查總部連根拔除&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1082740000t" end="1102650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;事成之後再解決她&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1111100000t" end="1164800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;沒錯&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;她是唯一知道KIRA的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1165830000t" end="1191080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;那就不能讓她活太久&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1197190000t" end="1213460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;扮演我的男友嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1214540000t" end="1234220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;一開始這樣也沒關係&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1235230000t" end="1275500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;那快點讓我看看你的死神吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1285610000t" end="1307560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;為了讓她相信我&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不得不這麼做嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1317980000t" end="1331970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;我知道了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1332990000t" end="1351990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;你能轉過去嗎&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;好的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1430760000t" end="1450670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;可以轉過來了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;好的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1473470000t" end="1482110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;你好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1501490000t" end="1534480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;雖然都是死神&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;但是跟雷姆完全不同耶&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1535530000t" end="1556800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;路克,我聽過你的名字&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1557880000t" end="1569820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;請多指教了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1570900000t" end="1583870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;好,請多指教&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1593920000t" end="1626910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;對了,月&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你知道殺死死神的方法嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1636960000t" end="1657550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;直接叫我月了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1658650000t" end="1688570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;不叫你月,叫你騎士可以嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1689680000t" end="1714020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;因為對我來說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你是我的白馬王子&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1720710000t" end="1731630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;叫月就好了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1746070000t" end="1777010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;這是22號&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;青山所有監視器的畫面&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1778100000t" end="1799710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;你想一個人看完嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1800790000t" end="1810110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;是的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1811140000t" end="1855170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;因為KIRA和第二KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;在這裡聯繫上的可能性很高&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1856180000t" end="1877790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;我想全部檢查一下&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1885550000t" end="1898170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;還有,夜神先生&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1899230000t" end="1911850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;是&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1912910000t" end="1952270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;請讓模木監視月的行動&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1953280000t" end="1972620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;月的行動?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1973630000t" end="1997970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;假如月就是KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1998990000t" end="2038010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;第二KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;應該會想辦法和KIRA碰面&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2047710000t" end="2056690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;我知道了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2072060000t" end="2104710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;不過龍崎到底是什麼時候睡覺的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2105770000t" end="2138080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;之前我看到他就以那姿勢睡著了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2153150000t" end="2169420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;相信我,是真的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2196860000t" end="2223480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;那麼,對特定的人產生愛意&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2224550000t" end="2262210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;如果為了延長那個人的壽命&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;而殺死別人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2263260000t" end="2283170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;死神就會死?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2284280000t" end="2292580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;沒錯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2316980000t" end="2353950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;我不認為有死神會那麼做&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2355010000t" end="2390960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;是啊&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;至少路克是絕對不會這麼做的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2397720000t" end="2444020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;另外,你之前的帶子&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;都是從哪裡寄到電視台的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2445100000t" end="2457040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;我想想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2458120000t" end="2499760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;最早是大阪,接著是東京&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;而之前是從長野&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2500830000t" end="2544170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;我都搭新幹線&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;讓人無法追蹤特定地點&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2545200000t" end="2593890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;沾有你朋友指紋的帶子和信封&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;還有剩吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2608600000t" end="2648530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;那些製作帶子所用過的東西&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;都要全部處理掉&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2655650000t" end="2710030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;可是要等明天從別處&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;最後一次寄帶子給電視台後再說&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2711040000t" end="2725030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;至於內容…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2735730000t" end="2760410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;不再以KIRA之名露面&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2761420000t" end="2799760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;謝謝警方的忠告&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2800790000t" end="2846410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;可是我將協助KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;制裁世上的罪惡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2847510000t" end="2874130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;讓KIRA認同我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2885880000t" end="2924220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;首先將制裁KIRA還沒制裁的罪犯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2925250000t" end="2990550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;然後將這股力量&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;分給配得上這股力量的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2991650000t" end="3018950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;藉以改變這個世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3020010000t" end="3039010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;分享力量?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3040030000t" end="3066310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;是用來擾亂他們搜查行動的手段&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3067390000t" end="3095030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;已經有了兩個擁有力量的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3096090000t" end="3119750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;再多幾個也不奇怪&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3120780000t" end="3149450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;他們認為這種人會一直增加&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;而感到焦慮&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3150480000t" end="3162420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;你能做到嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3163490000t" end="3191820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;不要問能做到嗎?&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;叫我做就行了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3192850000t" end="3219470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;我會對你言聽計從&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3220550000t" end="3240460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle82">&#x202a;另外還有一件很重要的事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3241570000t" end="3252830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle83">&#x202a;是&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3253910000t" end="3276890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle84">&#x202a;如果被警察抓到的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3277940000t" end="3300240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle85">&#x202a;即使只是嫌犯的身份&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3301290000t" end="3335650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle86">&#x202a;也不能提到彼此和筆記本的事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3336660000t" end="3378980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle87">&#x202a;只要沒有筆記本,他們就沒有證據&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3380040000t" end="3400290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle88">&#x202a;你能發誓做到嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3401390000t" end="3415040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle89">&#x202a;我發誓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3416070000t" end="3453380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle90">&#x202a;那麼這樣&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;男女朋友的契約就成立了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3454450000t" end="3466730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle91">&#x202a;算是這樣吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3474470000t" end="3494720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle92">&#x202a;那我也有條件&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3495820000t" end="3519480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle93">&#x202a;至少一周約會一次&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3531860000t" end="3552110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle94">&#x202a;這傢伙果然什麼都不明白&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3558220000t" end="3567890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle95">&#x202a;不可能的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3568890000t" end="3586520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle96">&#x202a;為什麼?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3587580000t" end="3613520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle97">&#x202a;我還以為不用解釋得這麼清楚的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3614610000t" end="3647600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle98">&#x202a;L已經開始懷疑我是KIRA了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3659980000t" end="3686600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle99">&#x202a;L真是厲害&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3687680000t" end="3735690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle100">&#x202a;大家都在說L什麼都不知道&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是個笨蛋什麼的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3736730000t" end="3754020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle101">&#x202a;其實他已經…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3755080000t" end="3777380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle102">&#x202a;不過或許是因禍得福&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3778440000t" end="3809380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle103">&#x202a;我也因此可以跟L直接接觸了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3817810000t" end="3844430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle104">&#x202a;L和KIRA已經彼此碰面了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3845500000t" end="3866090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle105">&#x202a;兩邊都好厲害&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3867190000t" end="3884480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle106">&#x202a;怎麼覺得好刺激喔&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3889880000t" end="3935500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle107">&#x202a;L認為就算我是KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不要洩漏本名就不會有危險&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3936590000t" end="3969580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle108">&#x202a;為了直接試探我&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;便以L的身份出現在我面前&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3991650000t" end="4032950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle109">&#x202a;只是因為沒其他可疑的對象&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4034020000t" end="4051990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle110">&#x202a;所以也只是猜測而已&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4053040000t" end="4082960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle111">&#x202a;因此只要我隱瞞得漂亮&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4084070000t" end="4111030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle112">&#x202a;可以讓他相信我&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;還能一起進行調查&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4112100000t" end="4154760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle113">&#x202a;那你把我帶到L那裡去就行了吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4160480000t" end="4180730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle114">&#x202a;沒那麼簡單的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4181840000t" end="4219500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle115">&#x202a;這麼靠近L,連我都應付得很辛苦&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4220540000t" end="4259560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle116">&#x202a;而且如果有人突然出現在我身邊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4260580000t" end="4305180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle117">&#x202a;KIRA和第二KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;對這個社會的態度又有變化的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4306300000t" end="4330640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle118">&#x202a;那你就會被懷疑是第二KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4331660000t" end="4366020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle119">&#x202a;而我是KIRA的嫌疑就更重了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4372700000t" end="4427310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle120">&#x202a;要是被認為我跟你突然認識&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;關係還如此親密就不好了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4428420000t" end="4445710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle121">&#x202a;我說的意思你明白嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4446770000t" end="4468040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle122">&#x202a;好像明白&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4469130000t" end="4490400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle123">&#x202a;所以才不能約會?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4491480000t" end="4521740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle124">&#x202a;因為害怕嫌疑會加深&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;所以不能見面嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4522850000t" end="4593500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle125">&#x202a;不,要先考慮不讓L知道你&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;又能讓你看到他的方式&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4609270000t" end="4631570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle126">&#x202a;除掉L需要你的幫忙&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4632620000t" end="4664930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle127">&#x202a;我們盡量見面時商量&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4665990000t" end="4678960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle128">&#x202a;太好了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4680000000t" end="4746670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle129">&#x202a;所以為了讓你不會太顯眼&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我也會常跟其他女孩見面&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4756080000t" end="4789070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle130">&#x202a;什麼意思?&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你也會跟其他女孩約會嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4790110000t" end="4803420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle131">&#x202a;就是這麼回事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4804460000t" end="4816740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle132">&#x202a;那不行&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4839830000t" end="4870430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle133">&#x202a;要是被我看到了,我就殺了那女孩&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4878540000t" end="4888430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle134">&#x202a;好可怕&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4894220000t" end="4907190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle135">&#x202a;我說,小海砂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4915570000t" end="4929900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle136">&#x202a;噁心的叫法…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4930920000t" end="4977910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle137">&#x202a;這不是遊戲&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我們要兩個人一起改變世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4984970000t" end="4998280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle138">&#x202a;話是沒錯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4999320000t" end="5032310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle139">&#x202a;但是我喜歡月,勝過這個世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5037360000t" end="5052030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle140">&#x202a;你在說什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5053040000t" end="5094680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle141">&#x202a;你應該是認同我才想跟我見面的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5095750000t" end="5121690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle142">&#x202a;而且我們才第一次見面吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5127780000t" end="5149050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle143">&#x202a;你曾經一見鍾情嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5150140000t" end="5161400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle144">&#x202a;沒有&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5162490000t" end="5220170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle145">&#x202a;我之前想見KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是因為感謝和認同,而不是愛&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5221210000t" end="5248850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle146">&#x202a;可是從我第一眼見到你,我就…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5249910000t" end="5271180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle147">&#x202a;這個女人是怎麼了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5272260000t" end="5292170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle148">&#x202a;你還是一樣很受歡迎嘛&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5298960000t" end="5334570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle149">&#x202a;那麼要是你喜歡我,就要聽我的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5335660000t" end="5358300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle150">&#x202a;一開始只是被利用也沒關係&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5359350000t" end="5386990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle151">&#x202a;你剛才也說過會對我言聽計從吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5388040000t" end="5421370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle152">&#x202a;但是我不允許你和別的女孩約會&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5422410000t" end="5443340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle153">&#x202a;這根本是兩回事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5453110000t" end="5486780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle154">&#x202a;現在兩本筆記本都在我手上&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5487810000t" end="5515790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle155">&#x202a;要是不聽我的,我就殺了你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5516840000t" end="5538110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle156">&#x202a;我不會允許的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5539200000t" end="5551820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle157">&#x202a;夜神月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5558880000t" end="5593460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle158">&#x202a;如果你殺了這個女孩&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5594580000t" end="5645550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle159">&#x202a;我就會在我的筆記本上&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;寫下你的名字殺死你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5657310000t" end="5695310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle160">&#x202a;我可以看到這個女孩的壽命&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5696350000t" end="5725360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle161">&#x202a;如果她提前死了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5726380000t" end="5753340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle162">&#x202a;我就會當成是你殺了她&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5754410000t" end="5798780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle163">&#x202a;如果你為了她而使用筆記本&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你不是也會死嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5799790000t" end="5828460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle164">&#x202a;對啊,這樣雷姆不就會死了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5833490000t" end="5853170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle165">&#x202a;確實是這樣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5854180000t" end="5880120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle166">&#x202a;但是我無所謂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5891550000t" end="5912140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle167">&#x202a;這個死神是怎麼回事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5913240000t" end="5940880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle168">&#x202a;他是認真的嗎?&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這樣的話就不好辦了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5949940000t" end="5959260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle169">&#x202a;月&#x202c;</p>
