<p begin="6021340000t" end="6042950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle172">&#x202a;怎麼把女孩子留到這麼晚&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6049370000t" end="6084640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle173">&#x202a;是啊,我們聊得都忘了時間&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6085740000t" end="6105420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle174">&#x202a;伯母,對不起&#x202c;</p>
