<p begin="7123440000t" end="7151080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle202">&#x202a;如果被知道她在跟我見面&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;會怎麼樣?&#x202c;</p>
