<p begin="8664320000t" end="8706300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle253">&#x202a;首先將制裁KIRA還沒制裁的罪犯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8707360000t" end="8743650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle254">&#x202a;然後將這股力量&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;分給配得上這股力量的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8744730000t" end="8766680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle255">&#x202a;藉以改變這個世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8794110000t" end="8847130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle256">&#x202a;我看了這個以後&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;覺得KIRA和第二KIRA聯繫上了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8862850000t" end="8879800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle257">&#x202a;為什麼這麼認為?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8880870000t" end="8902140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle258">&#x202a;你沒這種感覺嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8903220000t" end="8942240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle259">&#x202a;我還以為月會跟我有同樣的想法&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8967290000t" end="9016890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle260">&#x202a;首先是她拚命要見KIRA的態度&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;有了大轉變&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9018000000t" end="9046670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle261">&#x202a;還有現在才說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;為了讓KIRA認同自己&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9047700000t" end="9080690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle262">&#x202a;要制裁KIRA沒有制裁的罪犯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9101420000t" end="9127360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle263">&#x202a;為什麼之前都沒有那麼做呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9128450000t" end="9154730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle264">&#x202a;那是因為他沒有想到那麼多&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9167490000t" end="9198770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle265">&#x202a;恐怕是和KIRA聯繫上&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;聽他的命令做的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9209860000t" end="9254800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle266">&#x202a;然後被吩咐&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;隱瞞雙方已經聯繫上的事實&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9255910000t" end="9269900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle267">&#x202a;原來如此&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9270920000t" end="9306530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle268">&#x202a;那就是KIRA沒好好考慮過就行動&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9307630000t" end="9316950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle269">&#x202a;是的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9336990000t" end="9364290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle270">&#x202a;或是發生了讓他無法細想的事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9365350000t" end="9420300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle271">&#x202a;或故意讓我們知道他們聯繫上了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;藉此打擊我們的信心&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9421410000t" end="9447350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle272">&#x202a;事實上這的確是一大威脅&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9448430000t" end="9489040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle273">&#x202a;但是這樣一來&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;月是KIRA的嫌疑又降低了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9496150000t" end="9513100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle274">&#x202a;這是怎麼回事,龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9520840000t" end="9539150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle275">&#x202a;如果月是KIRA的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9540190000t" end="9569540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle276">&#x202a;不會要第二KIRA這麼做&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9570560000t" end="9630860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle277">&#x202a;應該會再次威脅L&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也就是逼我在電視上露臉&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9631950000t" end="9653900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle278">&#x202a;只要我們不知道他們已經聯繫上&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9654970000t" end="9678630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle279">&#x202a;責任就會全推到第二KIRA身上&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9699020000t" end="9716310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle280">&#x202a;再要他這麼說就行了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9737060000t" end="9760040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle281">&#x202a;「雖然曾經被KIRA阻止」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9761080000t" end="9797710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle282">&#x202a;「但我認為」&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;「那不是KIRA本人發出的勸告」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9798780000t" end="9825400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle283">&#x202a;「只要L死了,KIRA應該就會高興」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9826480000t" end="9847410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle284">&#x202a;「他不可能阻止我的」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9863850000t" end="9884440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle285">&#x202a;龍崎&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9885540000t" end="9923540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle286">&#x202a;如果我是KIRA,我不會那麼做&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9924580000t" end="9937890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle287">&#x202a;為什麼?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9938920000t" end="9981580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle288">&#x202a;龍崎是L的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我就知道L的個性&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9988640000t" end="10030620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle289">&#x202a;L不管受到任何恐嚇&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;都不會在電視上露面&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10031680000t" end="10058640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle290">&#x202a;也絕不會考慮找人來作替身&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10059710000t" end="10087690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle291">&#x202a;一定會考慮好什麼逃脫的手段&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10101750000t" end="10117670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle292">&#x202a;被你拆穿了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10118770000t" end="10129010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle293">&#x202a;月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10130110000t" end="10175730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle294">&#x202a;就算是舉例&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也不要說「如果我是KIRA」這種話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10180830000t" end="10197440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle295">&#x202a;對不起,爸爸&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10204520000t" end="10243200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle296">&#x202a;但是我希望對龍崎坦白&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10250570000t" end="10273890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle297">&#x202a;為了快點解決這案子&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10274930000t" end="10296540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle298">&#x202a;也為了洗清自己的嫌疑&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10297620000t" end="10350290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle299">&#x202a;而且正因為我不是KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我才敢說「如果我是KIRA」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10361350000t" end="10371240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle300">&#x202a;說的也是&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10378030000t" end="10393950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle301">&#x202a;月不是KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10395050000t" end="10426330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle302">&#x202a;不,月是KIRA的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我就傷腦筋了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10435750000t" end="10445420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle303">&#x202a;因為月…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10468120000t" end="10495080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle304">&#x202a;是我第一個朋友&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10579560000t" end="10622220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle305">&#x202a;是啊,對我來說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;龍崎也是一位相當投緣的朋友&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10638290000t" end="10647270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle306">&#x202a;多謝&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10668990000t" end="10695610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle307">&#x202a;你休學後讓我覺得很寂寞&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10703690000t" end="10724620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle308">&#x202a;真想再跟你打一場網球&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10735720000t" end="10751300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle309">&#x202a;好的,找機會&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10830150000t" end="10861430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle310">&#x202a;朋友?朋友嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10862510000t" end="10890490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle311">&#x202a;月,這不是很好嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10891540000t" end="10902460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle312">&#x202a;龍崎那傢伙&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10903550000t" end="10940520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle313">&#x202a;一下子就感覺到&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;KIRA和第二KIRA聯繫上了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10941590000t" end="10968210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle314">&#x202a;果然要盡快除掉他才行&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10976290000t" end="10986180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle315">&#x202a;是這樣嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10987300000t" end="11019270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle316">&#x202a;如此一來&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;和海砂見面的風險就更高了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11020340000t" end="11039340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle317">&#x202a;月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11059040000t" end="11083040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle318">&#x202a;我就是等不了兩個禮拜&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11084070000t" end="11108980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle319">&#x202a;現在正想去你家&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11132450000t" end="11175450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle320">&#x202a;我有生以來第一次這麼想打女人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11183170000t" end="11207510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle321">&#x202a;因為我很想見你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11220200000t" end="11245110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle322">&#x202a;算了,去我家吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11246230000t" end="11254530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle323">&#x202a;好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11296280000t" end="11310610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle324">&#x202a;又是女孩子&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11335990000t" end="11353960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle325">&#x202a;海砂小姐,歡迎你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11355010000t" end="11377650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle326">&#x202a;我看了好多你的照片&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11378700000t" end="11388940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle327">&#x202a;歡迎光臨&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11399050000t" end="11411670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle328">&#x202a;打擾了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11420740000t" end="11435980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle329">&#x202a;媽媽,茶&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11471790000t" end="11478040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle330">&#x202a;雷姆&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11492810000t" end="11518060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle331">&#x202a;你是站在海砂那一邊的吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11519170000t" end="11572530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle332">&#x202a;是啊,我從死神界&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;看過這孩子好多次了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11573560000t" end="11606210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle333">&#x202a;因為某個原因產生了一點感情&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11607260000t" end="11626940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle334">&#x202a;死神還會有感情啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11643630000t" end="11699260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle335">&#x202a;你好像對我之前那句話很不滿&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11700350000t" end="11741310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle336">&#x202a;只要海砂幸福,你也會高興嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11742390000t" end="11786990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle337">&#x202a;就是這個意思&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我不想看到她遭遇不幸&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11796110000t" end="11809080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle338">&#x202a;海砂是這麼的…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11830150000t" end="11847100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle339">&#x202a;喜歡我的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11848160000t" end="11857140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle340">&#x202a;月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11862510000t" end="11881850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle341">&#x202a;海砂&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11882870000t" end="11913810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle342">&#x202a;只要我幸福,你就幸福嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11941590000t" end="11958880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle343">&#x202a;你可以拜託雷姆嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11959940000t" end="11975520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle344">&#x202a;請雷姆殺死L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11987970000t" end="12013220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle345">&#x202a;因為雷姆也希望你幸福&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12014330000t" end="12062000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle346">&#x202a;不論我們誰被L抓到&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;都會陷入不幸&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12080400000t" end="12124430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle347">&#x202a;死神不能告訴人類他人的名字&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12125440000t" end="12162070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle348">&#x202a;但是雷姆要殺誰都是不受限制的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12163150000t" end="12193750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle349">&#x202a;是啊,如果你能殺死L的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12194840000t" end="12236820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle350">&#x202a;我會覺得海砂更加可愛&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也會感謝你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12237890000t" end="12267240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle351">&#x202a;最重要的是我們兩個都能幸福&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12268250000t" end="12301240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle352">&#x202a;雷姆,我希望月能愛著我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12302280000t" end="12323550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle353">&#x202a;我們兩個都會高興&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12324640000t" end="12344550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle354">&#x202a;那就是我的幸福了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12467120000t" end="12475420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle355">&#x202a;好吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12490140000t" end="12512440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle356">&#x202a;好吧,夜神月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12513500000t" end="12532840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle357">&#x202a;我討厭你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12533850000t" end="12574460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle358">&#x202a;就算結果是延長了你的壽命&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我也不會死&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12580560000t" end="12599210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle359">&#x202a;我去殺了L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12605590000t" end="12643250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle360">&#x202a;我根本不在乎L是生是死&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12644290000t" end="12659530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle361">&#x202a;太好了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12660640000t" end="12681910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle362">&#x202a;雷姆,謝謝你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12683000000t" end="12698240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle363">&#x202a;不愧是雷姆&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12714360000t" end="12728010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle364">&#x202a;L要死了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12738390000t" end="12751360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle365">&#x202a;這麼簡單…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12805120000t" end="12855400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle366">&#x202a;看見誰都無法看見的夢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12856510000t" end="12910210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle367">&#x202a;捨棄所有不需要的事物&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12911230000t" end="12943200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle368">&#x202a;無法割捨的感情&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12944260000t" end="12998640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle369">&#x202a;深藏在我的心裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12999650000t" end="13063360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle370">&#x202a;依然處在現實與理想的夾縫中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13064380000t" end="13115350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle371">&#x202a;即使犧牲的伽鎖拴住敢的腳&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13116430000t" end="13166710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle372">&#x202a;無法壓抑滿腔的衝動&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13167820000t" end="13235850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle373">&#x202a;因為我有一顆強烈追求的心&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13245560000t" end="13293230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle374">&#x202a;虛偽恐懼虛飾憂愁&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13294280000t" end="13348660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle375">&#x202a;面對各種負面情緒&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13349660000t" end="13403700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle376">&#x202a;我也不會弱到被擊垮&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13404720000t" end="13449090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle377">&#x202a;不知孤獨為何物Trickster&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13510830000t" end="13548490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle378">&#x202a;沒錯&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;流河自稱是L就該殺了他&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13549530000t" end="13562500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle379">&#x202a;這已經是一場賭注了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13577890000t" end="13590170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle380">&#x202a;明天將是L.二&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13591240000t" end="13623550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle381">&#x202a;不,至少是龍崎流河的忌日&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13632280000t" end="13651280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle382">&#x202a;下一回,賭注&#x202c;</p>
